<strong>BIBLIOGRAPHY ENTRY</strong>
<br><br>
References to the Bible and other sacred scriptures appear only in footnotes or in&#45;text citations. The Bible is not listed as a book in your bibliography. However, if you have a lot of biblical references in your writing, you may indicate the version you used at the beginning of your Bibliography. 
<br><br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref">
	References to the Bible are taken from the New Revised Standard Version.
</blockquote>
